  <brief_title>A Pilot Study of the Envision® Surface</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Pilot Study of the Envision® Surface in a Patient Population at High Risk for or Who Have Pressure Ulcers: Evaluation of Pressure Ulcer Incidence, Changes in Existing Pressure Ulcers, Clinical Staff Satisfaction and Patient Comfort</official_title>
  <sponsors>
