  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is to evaluate the clinical safety and effectiveness of the Envision® surface.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study is to evaluate the clinical safety and effectiveness of the Envision® surface
      placed on the TotalCare® frame in pressure ulcer prevention and management, patient comfort,
      and staff acceptance in the critical care environment
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
